{"tid":1379791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咁多人唔明點解公務員要8月2先集會唔罷工住？","createTime":"2019-07-29T00:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T05:10:58.000Z","uid":5600,"like":105,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"393ae6f86444cfd17aae1edad2796506824d0542","tid":1379791,"uid":5600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:33:07.000Z","msg":"做得公務員好多都係求安穩求穩定<br />\n你要知道佢地係最想補住份工既人<br />\n要佢地有決心罷工<br />\n首先佢地自己要知道有幾多公務員係同路人<br />\n8月2佢地晒冷就係要打支強心針 亦可以即場傾下罷工大方向<br />\n8月5佢地先敢去做罷工呢步 <br />\n唔好再話集會冇用 佢地公務員應該即時罷工<br />\n俾少少時間人跳出個comfort zobe"},{"pid":"d82aa18a4cdfbc98fe8ea43e7b5d12abc5408f91","tid":1379791,"uid":6528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:34:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n2047到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！"},{"pid":"dd6bcb36c2a2dcc78fe340a04ac1b40ef039cb3c","tid":1379791,"uid":14520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:34:26.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"3b03bf88f7acb607806493ae542cda50e7b09c3e","tid":1379791,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:35:25.000Z","msg":"人地集會，從來沒有講過會罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba9aabfd1e31d4cc65200af8b6aa5d46f936f4f1","tid":1379791,"uid":5600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b03bf88f7acb607806493ae542cda50e7b09c3e","tid":1379791,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:35:25.000Z","msg":"人地集會，從來沒有講過會罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:36:21.000Z","msg":"當大家有共識8月5全港罷工既<br />\n當場一定有人會講"},{"pid":"c176e73cff6854c19ee29deb0ac1a1e0b3511a56","tid":1379791,"uid":50414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:37:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"063f6affd2ad70c85993e57f754bae7daf6963fd","tid":1379791,"uid":239250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:39:23.000Z","msg":"建議不要只睇熱門"},{"pid":"ac6d0e20f3e937e798362d479b9725aa152301d0","tid":1379791,"uid":38237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:46:30.000Z","msg":"--------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打爆啲交通燈會唔會易過全民死火燈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1377458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1377458</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------"},{"pid":"60f0e630444c20f275d5975d0d5517c78deef779","tid":1379791,"uid":7738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:47:53.000Z","msg":"正確"},{"pid":"cb2e9bde095a16f03fa44ed231a6c691a794a53b","tid":1379791,"uid":260335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:49:12.000Z","msg":"要罷工一定要團結 要d時間醞釀 <br />\n希望大家明白 同呢幾日多d支